WEBVTT

00:02.369 --> 00:03.401
[ Remote clicks ]

00:03.403 --> 00:04.937
[ Upbeat music plays ]

00:07.508 --> 00:10.376
♪ I don't care what you say! ♪

00:11.712 --> 00:13.712
♪ I'm gonna do what I want
all day! ♪

00:13.714 --> 00:16.348
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:16.350 --> 00:18.250
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:18.252 --> 00:22.688
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:22.743 --> 00:23.846
♪♪

00:23.848 --> 00:26.949
Clarence: I'm the great
master of Mount Dragoon!

00:26.951 --> 00:28.451
You killed my brother.

00:28.453 --> 00:30.019
Prepare to die.

00:30.021 --> 00:32.188
Man on TV:<i> Flaming finger!</i>

00:32.190 --> 00:33.289
Hyah!

00:33.291 --> 00:34.924
[ Grunts ]

00:34.926 --> 00:36.792
[ Both laugh ]

00:36.794 --> 00:38.594
Oh.
Fiddlesticks.

00:38.596 --> 00:40.596
Kevin: Oh,
that was St. Patrick's Day.

00:40.598 --> 00:42.564
I got to add this one
to my scrapbook.

00:42.566 --> 00:47.036
Um, the TV just stopped
working, um, for no reason.

00:47.038 --> 00:48.537
[ Lips squeak ]

00:48.539 --> 00:50.706
You just got to make sure
it's plugged in all the way.

00:50.708 --> 00:52.208
Here.

00:52.210 --> 00:53.075
Both: Yay!

00:53.077 --> 00:54.276
[ Telephone rings ]

00:54.278 --> 00:56.111
Uh-huh, yeah.
Sure. Just the bangs?

00:56.113 --> 00:57.480
Uh-huh.
- Uh, Mom?

00:57.482 --> 00:59.982
Okay, great. Yeah, see you there
at 3:00 on Thursday.

00:59.984 --> 01:01.551
Okay, bye-bye.

01:01.553 --> 01:04.720
[ Muffled ] Mom, um, can we get
a ride to Mount Dragoon?

01:04.722 --> 01:07.723
Sure. I'll, uh,
I'll look up directions.

01:07.725 --> 01:08.657
Both: Yay!

01:08.659 --> 01:09.959
Okay.

01:11.996 --> 01:13.830
Oh, hey, honey.

01:13.832 --> 01:16.232
I got a little surprise
for you.

01:16.234 --> 01:18.133
Oh, my...

01:18.135 --> 01:19.902
Crab style.

01:19.904 --> 01:21.503
Snake style.

01:21.505 --> 01:23.272
You killed my brother.

01:23.274 --> 01:25.574
Prepare to die!

01:25.576 --> 01:27.343
Thanks, Mom.
- Oh, you're welcome.

01:27.345 --> 01:29.445
Hey, don't forget
- to wear your pants, too.

01:30.748 --> 01:33.615
And you know what? That's not
the<i> only</i> surprise I got you.

01:33.617 --> 01:35.951
I signed you up
for karate lessons.

01:35.953 --> 01:37.653
[ Thud ]

01:37.655 --> 01:38.354
What?

01:38.356 --> 01:39.321
Whoa!

01:39.323 --> 01:40.255
Oh...

01:40.257 --> 01:41.423
...my...

01:41.425 --> 01:43.526
Are you also
doing karate, too?

01:44.695 --> 01:45.827
Yaaah!

01:45.829 --> 01:47.263
[ Laughs ] Oh, no.

01:47.265 --> 01:48.264
[ Both grunting ]

01:48.266 --> 01:50.265
Exploding fist!

01:50.267 --> 01:52.768
Ohhhh! You got me!

01:52.770 --> 01:53.836
Sweet revenge.

01:53.838 --> 01:56.638
Okay, young ones.
Settle down.

01:56.640 --> 01:59.374
Wow. Are you gonna teach us
how to kick butt?

01:59.376 --> 02:01.543
Martial arts
is a meaningful practice.

02:01.545 --> 02:03.212
It's about
discipline and --

02:03.214 --> 02:04.847
I'm gonna be
a black belt.

02:04.849 --> 02:08.117
You must earn
your yellow belt first.

02:08.119 --> 02:09.885
I'm gonna be
a yellow belt.

02:09.887 --> 02:13.389
Sumo-san,
do you need a gi?

02:13.391 --> 02:14.623
Nah, I'm cool.

02:14.625 --> 02:16.792
Well, you can't wear
the headband --

02:16.794 --> 02:17.460
[ Growls ]

02:17.462 --> 02:18.994
Okay, have fun, boys.

02:18.996 --> 02:19.996
Join us.

02:19.998 --> 02:22.632
Me? But isn't this
a kids' class?

02:22.634 --> 02:25.067
We accept fledglings
of<i> all</i> ages.

02:25.069 --> 02:26.301
[ Grunts ]

02:26.303 --> 02:27.569
Ooh!

02:27.571 --> 02:30.239
Well, it sounds fun,
but my -- my clothes --

02:30.241 --> 02:33.375
I'll give you
a $10 discount.

02:33.377 --> 02:34.577
My, oh, me,
I love this gi!

02:34.579 --> 02:35.844
All right, Mom!

02:35.846 --> 02:37.713
We're the masters
of Mount Dragoon!

02:37.715 --> 02:38.747
Kapow!

02:38.749 --> 02:40.349
[ Snores ]

02:40.351 --> 02:43.352
The importance
of exercising restraint

02:43.354 --> 02:45.254
and controlling our feelings

02:45.256 --> 02:49.925
all comes down to honoring
our number-one tenet...

02:49.927 --> 02:51.194
[ Squeaking ]

02:51.196 --> 02:52.561
...discipline.

02:52.563 --> 02:54.697
Oh. Discipline.

02:54.699 --> 02:58.267
Oh! But if a bunch of bad guys
busted in here like,

02:58.269 --> 03:00.102
"Oh, no!
They're gonna kill us!"

03:00.104 --> 03:03.505
we could grab all the swords
and just start swordfighting

03:03.507 --> 03:05.874
until there's one guy left,
and I'm like,

03:05.876 --> 03:07.777
"Wait! He killed
my brother!"

03:07.779 --> 03:09.444
and he has a scar
on his face --

03:09.446 --> 03:11.947
Where's your worksheet?

03:11.949 --> 03:13.783
Oh. You mean...

03:13.785 --> 03:15.217
Hyah!

03:15.219 --> 03:17.386
♪♪

03:19.022 --> 03:19.955
[ Laughs ]

03:19.957 --> 03:21.290
[ Growling ]

03:21.292 --> 03:25.428
Now we're going to try
something quite exciting --

03:25.430 --> 03:27.129
sand grabbing.

03:27.131 --> 03:31.967
Everyone line up and await
your turn to touch sand.

03:31.969 --> 03:33.902
Wow. This feels
kind of nice.

03:33.904 --> 03:36.972
Sensei Carlos:
The sand represents...

03:36.974 --> 03:38.474
sand.

03:38.476 --> 03:39.808
[ Whispering ]
Hey, Sumo.

03:39.810 --> 03:43.612
Now for something
even more thrilling.

03:43.614 --> 03:47.149
Though we won't really
be touching the board today,

03:47.151 --> 03:49.651
but it's here
for psychological reasons.

03:49.653 --> 03:52.454
I will take your village
and karate-chop your livestock!

03:52.456 --> 03:53.455
[ Laughs ]

03:53.457 --> 03:54.990
[ Clears throat ]

03:54.992 --> 03:58.593
Would you two like
to rejoin the class?

03:58.595 --> 04:01.330
Who would like
to go first?

04:01.332 --> 04:03.566
Hyah!

04:03.568 --> 04:05.467
If you had
really hit the board,

04:05.469 --> 04:08.437
you would've broken
every bone in your hand.

04:08.439 --> 04:10.339
Ooh!

04:10.341 --> 04:11.773
[ Grunts ]

04:11.775 --> 04:14.977
Impressively gentle,
Mavis.

04:14.979 --> 04:17.513
Hyyyyyy...ah!

04:17.515 --> 04:20.015
Very good, fledgling.

04:20.017 --> 04:22.151
Thanks. [ Chuckles ]

04:22.153 --> 04:24.520
[ Grunts ]

04:24.522 --> 04:27.489
That would've broken the board
clean through.

04:27.491 --> 04:29.024
[ Sniffs ]

04:29.026 --> 04:30.159
Yeah, whatever.

04:30.161 --> 04:32.461
[ Both grunting ]

04:32.463 --> 04:33.996
<i>Aah!</i>

04:33.998 --> 04:36.799
Mrs. Sammy, uh,
is Mary on break?

04:36.801 --> 04:38.334
She's gonna
- give me some highlights.

04:38.336 --> 04:41.370
She's in karate with Clarence.
It's around the corner.

04:41.372 --> 04:43.139
Breathe in.

04:43.141 --> 04:44.540
[ All inhale ]

04:44.542 --> 04:46.642
And let it out.

04:46.644 --> 04:48.710
[ All exhale ]

04:48.712 --> 04:51.380
[ Straining ]
One more time.

04:51.382 --> 04:52.648
[ All inhale ]

04:52.650 --> 04:54.316
[ Bell jingles ]

04:54.318 --> 04:55.884
Uh, e-excuse me.

04:55.886 --> 04:57.886
Are you interested
in a class?

04:57.888 --> 05:00.022
No, no, not really.
I just need to, uh --

05:00.024 --> 05:02.224
Actually,
can I just watch?

05:02.226 --> 05:04.326
Of course.

05:04.328 --> 05:06.561
There is
a $2 auditing fee.

05:06.563 --> 05:08.364
That's odd.

05:08.366 --> 05:10.066
[ Grunting ]
Chop, chop!

05:10.068 --> 05:11.800
[ Bird shrieks ]

05:11.802 --> 05:13.368
Oh!

05:13.370 --> 05:22.911
♪♪

05:22.913 --> 05:23.712
Hyyyyah!

05:23.714 --> 05:24.646
[ Crack ]
Ohh!

05:24.648 --> 05:26.515
[ Growling ]

05:26.517 --> 05:28.584
[ Both laughing ]

05:29.853 --> 05:31.587
Hyah!

05:31.589 --> 05:35.390
[ All grunting ]

05:35.392 --> 05:38.160
Drop it! Drop it!
Drop it!

05:38.162 --> 05:40.930
You showed
great potential today.

05:40.932 --> 05:43.866
You could be a master,
Mary-san.

05:43.868 --> 05:45.834
Mary: You know,
the class is really fun,

05:45.836 --> 05:48.170
and I think Clarence and I
are getting the hang of it.

05:48.172 --> 05:49.438
I don't know, Mom.

05:49.440 --> 05:52.207
Sensei Carlos looks like
he's just sleeping all the time,

05:52.209 --> 05:53.742
not teaching.

05:53.744 --> 05:54.843
Boop!
- Aah!

05:54.845 --> 05:56.177
Masters never sleep.
- [ Laughs ]

05:56.179 --> 05:58.781
They just pretend
so they can eat you alive!

05:58.783 --> 06:00.181
Pbht!

06:00.183 --> 06:02.050
Oh, man.
I'm a lucky man.

06:02.052 --> 06:03.119
[ Camera clicks ]

06:04.955 --> 06:05.787
[ Gasps ]

06:05.789 --> 06:07.689
♪ Choo-choo ♪
- Whoa!

06:07.691 --> 06:08.790
Mom!
Did you see that?!

06:08.792 --> 06:10.426
Come on.
We're gonna be late.

06:10.428 --> 06:12.461
[ Note plays ]

06:12.463 --> 06:14.196
All: Ohmm.

06:14.198 --> 06:15.631
[ Snores ]

06:15.633 --> 06:16.632
Huh? What?

06:16.634 --> 06:20.135
All: Ohmm.

06:20.137 --> 06:21.437
[ Notes continue ]

06:21.439 --> 06:23.739
Psst. Want to ride
the train?

06:23.741 --> 06:25.273
Yes, I do.

06:25.275 --> 06:29.311
Sensei Carlos, um, are we
gonna fight some bad guys?

06:29.313 --> 06:30.879
No.

06:30.881 --> 06:33.081
All right, then. We got to go
to the bathroom!

06:33.083 --> 06:35.317
Wait, Clarence!

06:35.319 --> 06:36.318
Ohmm.

06:36.320 --> 06:39.922
All: Ohmm.

06:41.225 --> 06:46.061
All: Ohmm.

06:46.063 --> 06:49.798
[ Both laugh ]

06:49.800 --> 06:51.967
Clarence, how come
you left class?

06:51.969 --> 06:54.969
Mm, Sensei Carlos
- just talks the whole time,

06:54.971 --> 06:56.338
and it is
kind of boring.

06:56.340 --> 06:58.840
He can be long-winded,
but we can't stop going now.

06:58.842 --> 07:01.143
You know, we're supposed
to be dragon masters!

07:01.145 --> 07:02.844
It's Masters
of Mount Dragoon.

07:02.846 --> 07:06.014
Well, masters of whatever.
We're having fun, right?

07:06.016 --> 07:07.516
I don't want to go
anymore.

07:07.518 --> 07:08.517
Come on, Clarence.

07:08.519 --> 07:10.519
I don't want to.

07:10.521 --> 07:12.688
Too bad.
We're going.

07:15.426 --> 07:17.660
[ Laughs ]

07:18.796 --> 07:20.262
Everything okay
with him, Mary?

07:20.264 --> 07:22.197
Oh, he's just being
a little butt.

07:22.199 --> 07:23.698
Okay, fledglings.

07:23.700 --> 07:26.635
I believe
you are finally ready.

07:26.637 --> 07:28.871
[ Murmuring excitedly ]

07:28.873 --> 07:32.207
Today, I will end you.

07:32.209 --> 07:33.475
Hyah!

07:33.477 --> 07:34.476
Oh!

07:34.478 --> 07:35.778
[ Laughs ]

07:38.382 --> 07:39.447
Excuse me!

07:39.449 --> 07:41.216
[ Laughs, snorts ]

07:41.218 --> 07:43.619
[ Grunts ]

07:43.621 --> 07:46.222
[ Laughs ]

07:46.224 --> 07:47.889
Very impressive.

07:47.891 --> 07:49.391
Allow me to fetch another --

07:49.393 --> 07:50.559
Mary: Wait!

07:50.561 --> 07:53.161
♪♪

07:53.163 --> 07:56.498
[ Exhales ]

07:56.500 --> 07:57.565
Hah...

07:57.567 --> 07:58.734
Kaboom!

07:58.736 --> 07:59.668
[ Gasps ]

07:59.670 --> 08:00.736
[ Groans ]

08:00.738 --> 08:03.638
Astounding progress,
Mary-san.

08:03.640 --> 08:05.340
Clarence?
Hey, Clarence!

08:05.342 --> 08:06.542
Did you see that?

08:06.544 --> 08:08.077
No, I did not.

08:08.079 --> 08:10.212
Clarence, why are you
being like this?

08:10.214 --> 08:12.381
Where are you going?
Don't roll away from me!

08:12.383 --> 08:13.748
I don't like it.

08:13.750 --> 08:15.750
I don't like boring karate.
It's boring.

08:15.752 --> 08:18.086
What?! We beat
the splinters out of it,

08:18.088 --> 08:19.721
just what
you always wanted.

08:19.723 --> 08:21.690
No!
That's what<i> you</i> wanted.

08:21.692 --> 08:23.926
[ Grunting ]

08:23.928 --> 08:27.263
[ Sighs ] I thought we were
gonna be dragon masters.

08:27.265 --> 08:28.564
Mount Dragoon.

08:28.566 --> 08:30.899
Ugh. Fine! If you hate it
so much, you can quit.

08:30.901 --> 08:33.735
But don't you care
that<i> I</i> like it?

08:33.737 --> 08:34.736
[ Sizzling ]

08:34.738 --> 08:36.171
[ Doorbell rings ]

08:36.173 --> 08:38.406
Hey, Chad, can you get the door?
I think they're here.

08:38.408 --> 08:39.741
Oh, coming!

08:39.743 --> 08:41.777
♪♪

08:41.779 --> 08:44.046
What do we have here?

08:44.048 --> 08:45.181
Aww!

08:46.750 --> 08:48.784
Aww, look at those guys.

08:48.786 --> 08:50.619
Oh.

08:50.621 --> 08:52.888
Aww, that was fun.

08:54.024 --> 08:56.525
That was
my first day at school.

08:56.527 --> 08:59.027
Lot of me's in here.

08:59.029 --> 09:01.697
There goes all my hair.

09:01.699 --> 09:03.298
[ Laughs ]

09:03.300 --> 09:12.641
♪♪

09:12.643 --> 09:15.644
[ Chad grunting ] Come on, Chad. You got
to get your left hand over to blue.

09:15.646 --> 09:17.446
[ Laughter ]

09:20.651 --> 09:22.484
[ Indistinct conversation ]

09:22.486 --> 09:25.087
All: Ohmm.

09:25.089 --> 09:27.389
Sensei Carlos:
Congratulations, class.

09:27.391 --> 09:28.891
Today, you transform

09:28.893 --> 09:32.627
from lowly fledglings
into seedlings,

09:32.629 --> 09:35.163
and how ni-- how nice...
Oh, yeah!

09:35.165 --> 09:39.835
...it truly is to share this
moment with your loved ones.

09:39.837 --> 09:41.670
[ Fly buzzing ]

09:41.672 --> 09:42.571
[ Sighs ]

09:42.573 --> 09:43.505
Oh!

09:43.507 --> 09:44.973
Congratulations, Mary-san.

09:44.975 --> 09:46.508
Clarence:
Stop the ceremony!

09:46.510 --> 09:47.742
Aah!

09:47.744 --> 09:50.178
Um, h-hey, Mar.
Congrats.

09:50.180 --> 09:51.012
Clarence?

09:51.014 --> 09:52.780
Oh. Oh, hey, guys.

09:52.782 --> 09:54.349
Coming through.
Excuse me.

09:54.351 --> 09:55.651
Proceed.

09:55.653 --> 09:57.685
All...right.

09:57.687 --> 09:59.654
Here you are, Mary-san.

09:59.656 --> 10:00.823
Oh, yeah!

10:00.825 --> 10:03.158
You got the yellowest belt
in town!

10:03.160 --> 10:03.858
Whoo!

10:03.860 --> 10:05.093
Go, Mary!

10:05.095 --> 10:07.930
And now,
for everyone's viewing pleasure,

10:07.932 --> 10:12.534
our two strongest students
shall fight.

10:12.536 --> 10:15.771
[ Grunting ]

10:15.773 --> 10:17.673
<i>I'm</i> number one!

10:17.675 --> 10:18.874
Oh!

10:18.876 --> 10:20.142
[ Grunts ]

10:20.144 --> 10:21.976
Don't mess
with a Dragoon Warrior.

10:21.978 --> 10:24.513
[ Hard rock music plays ]

10:24.515 --> 10:25.714
Uhhhh!

10:25.716 --> 10:26.881
Oh!

10:26.883 --> 10:28.050
I love you.

10:28.052 --> 10:29.851
Aww, I love you, too,
Clarence.

10:29.853 --> 10:31.653
Hey, Sumo,
did you see my mom?

10:31.655 --> 10:33.221
[ Indistinct conversations ]

10:33.223 --> 10:36.324
My mom has beat up
over 100 bad guys.

10:36.326 --> 10:39.294
And her name is Mom.
She is my mom.

10:39.296 --> 10:42.030
She feeds me
- and also she kills people.

10:42.032 --> 10:44.066
One last bit
of housekeeping.

10:44.068 --> 10:48.737
Some of you still owe me
for classes.

10:48.739 --> 10:53.241
This is your last chance
to pay up.

10:53.243 --> 10:56.411
I got your money
right here.

10:56.413 --> 10:57.379
Aaah!        Aaah!

10:58.714 --> 11:00.549
♪ Early to bed ♪

11:02.085 --> 11:04.186
♪ Early to rise ♪

11:05.722 --> 11:07.723
♪ Picking my nose ♪
